         <div type="translation"
              ana="#b1"
              xml:id="zoor0357.translation"
              corresp="#zoor0357.transcription">
            <p>One (is) the God, Jesus Christ. Monument of His servant Valentina, who died
                    having a good name and good...</p>
         </div>
